    Verse: 7
Tags:
  - Teacher
---
The teacher can show you the way. The teacher can inspire you. The teacher
can try to give you a little bit of enthusiasm and courage. But you will
have to keep your feet yourself on every rung of the spiritual ladder. The
teacher cannot do it for you.
